<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4951984>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 18. Lamispina chilensis n. sp. A. Holotype (USNM 56470) and paratype (USNM 1251914), holotype at left in dorsal view, head exposed, paratype in left lateral view. B. Paratype (USNM 1251914), anterior end, right lateral view. C. Paratype (USNM 1251915), chaetiger 18, cross section. D. Same, long papilla and notochaetal basal and medial regions. E. Same, chaetiger 15, left parapodium, lamispines. F. Same, basal, medial and distal regions. Scale bars: A: 0.9 mm, B: 0.3 mm, C, E: 0.1 mm, D: 50 µm, F: 35 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4951984/files/figure.png" .

